msgctxt "sn29.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 29 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 29 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Nāgavagga "
msgstr "1. Dragons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Dutiyasutasutta → tassa sutam 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn29.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Dutiyasutasutta "
msgstr "8. They’ve Heard (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.244, sc1
msgctxt "sn29.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.8:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.8:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā jalābujānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the womb-born dragons?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.8:1.4"
msgid "… pe … "
msgstr "(All should be told in full.) "

msgctxt "sn29.8:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā jalābujānaṃ nāgānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn29.8:1.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
